interpretation: The "woman rowing boat" card represents a journey or voyage that requires hard work and determination. The woman in the boat is the embodiment of focus and strength, powering through the rough waters ahead. This card suggests that you are in a transitional phase in your life, and you need to be prepared to put in the effort to reach your destination. It may be a time of struggle and challenges, but with perseverance, you can overcome any obstacles. You may be called upon to take on a leadership role or to navigate through uncharted waters. Trust your instincts and rely on your inner strength to guide you through this journey. This card reminds you that the journey is just as important as the destination, and that the lessons you learn along the way will be valuable in your future endeavors.
